# Jobflow

A distributed job queue system built with Node.js, BullMQ, Redis, and PostgreSQL.

## Features
- Priority-based job scheduling
- Exponential backoff retries
- Dead letter queue recovery
- Real-time WebSocket updates
- JWT-based role access
- PostgreSQL audit logging

## Tech Stack
- **Backend:** Node.js, Express
- **Queue:** BullMQ, Redis
- **Database:** PostgreSQL, Drizzle ORM
- **Auth:** JWT
- **Testing:** Jest, Supertest

## Getting Started

### Prerequisites
- Docker
- Docker Compose

### Run locally
git clone https://github.com/ragav/jobflow
cd jobflow/backend